Risks & Countermeasures

1. Schedule Inconsistency
-plan in less detail for long term plan,
-And higher detail for short term plan

2. Change of Requirements
-shorter intervals between requirement gathering
-constant reassessment of current requirements

3. Data Loss
(hard drive failure, cloud back-up service down)
-backup plan

4. Miscommunication and Language Barrier
-communicate in a more simple format
-make sure everyone understand the topic before proceeding to the next

